data.meta_description: Poet, Author, Director, Screenwriter, Actor. One of Sweden´s intellectual leaders. A ”multi-doer” with a predilection for words. Lyrics and poems containing subtle humour was Tage Danielsson´s distinctive feature. In 1956 he met Hans Alfredson, with whom he began a lifelong partnership. Together, as ”HasseåTage” they...
